Package: tidytags
Title: Easy Collection and Powerful Analysis of Twitter Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Staudt Willet", "K. Bret", email = "bret@bretsw.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Rosenberg", "Joshua M.", email = "jmrosenberg@utk.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Greenhalgh", "Spencer P.", email = "spencer.greenhalgh@uky.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Description: The goal of tidytags is to sync together 
    (a) the ease of collecting tweets over time with a 
    **Twitter Archiving Google Sheet** [TAGS](https://tags.hawksey.info/), 
    (b) the utility of the **rtweet** [package](https://rtweet.info/) for 
    processing and preparing additional Twitter metadata, and 
    (c) a collection of different analytic functions we have developed 
    during our own social media research.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/bretsw/tidytags
